‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ

final_score = base √ó company_mult √ó position_mult
base = (tag_rel √ó tag_weight) + (priority/10 √ó pri_weight)
company_mult = 0.8 + (priority/10) √ó 0.4
position_mult = priority_mult √ó tag_mult
